    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The only difference between isBlank() and isEmpty() is:</p>\n\n<pre><code>StringUtils.isBlank(\" \")       = true //compared string value has space and considered as blank\n\nStringUtils.isEmpty(\" \")       = false //compared string value has space and not considered as empty\n</code></pre>\n"
